[[module CSS]]
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Nova+Flat');

.image-container > .image {
    margin: 1em auto;
    border-radius: 10px;
}

#page-title {
  display: none;
}

.skysermon-nav {
    color: #fff000;
    text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.35);
    border-radius: 1px;
    border: double 3px #fff000;
    background-color: #c70030;
    box-shadow: 1.5px 1.5px 3px #636ce9;
    padding: 0 30px;
    margin: 10px 0 15px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.skysermon-nav a{
    color: #fff000;
}
div.content-panel.standalone.series div.image-container.aligncenter::before {
    content: "SKY SERMON";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'Nova Flat', cursive;
    font-size: 400%;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: white;
    text-shadow: 0.25rem 0.188rem 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.15), 0.563rem 0.5rem 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
}

div.content-panel.standalone.series div.image-container.aligncenter {
    position: relative;
}

@media only screen and (max-width: 768px) {
	div.content-panel.standalone.series div.image-container.aligncenter::before {
		font-size: 200%;
	}
}
[[/module]]

[[include theme:black-highlighter-theme]]
[[include :scp-wiki:theme:ch-scp-theme]]

[[div class="content-panel standalone series"]]
[[=]]
[[=image https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a5/Andromeda_galaxy_Ssc2005-20a1.jpg/1530px-Andromeda_galaxy_Ssc2005-20a1.jpg]]
[[span style="font-family: 'Nova Flat', cursive;";]]
A storm is brewing in China -- in the dingy slums, the bright halls of the Foundation, and the cold darkness of space. GoI-084, an army of internet-dwelling cultists calling themselves "The Galactic Federation", haunt the forgotten corners of Geocities and Web 1.0, praying to something floating in the nothing that is the void. The Foundation, being well-versed in dealing with cultists, handle this new threat by the books. After all, cults have been fooling themselves into belief for time immemorial. 

That's why they never consider if the cult is right.
[[/span]]
@@ @@
-----
   [[div class="content-panel standalone series"]]
[[span style="font-family: 'Nova Flat', cursive; font-size: 150%";]]
**Chapter I**
@@ @@
//The mind is everything. What you think, you become.//
[[/span]]
[[span style="font-family: 'Nova Flat', cursive; font-size: 120%";]]
☸[[[aflame-with-the-fires-of-delusion|Aflame with the Fires of Delusion]]]☸
[[/span]]
[[span style="font-family: 'Nova Flat', cursive";]]"Then, maybe, he will stare upon the form of the true Buddha as He leans His golden head, displaying the truth of Dana, and pulls Bat's being into nothing."[[/span]]
[[span style="font-family: 'Nova Flat', cursive; font-size: 120%";]]
☸[[[oh-i-feel-it-i-feel-the-cosmos|Oh, I feel it! I feel the cosmos!]]]☸
[[/span]]
[[span style="font-family: 'Nova Flat', cursive";]]"Join us join us join us join us join us the Buddha waits join us join us join us join us"[[/span]]
[[span style="font-family: 'Nova Flat', cursive; font-size: 120%";]]
☸[[[scp-4161|SCP-4161 - METEMPSYCHOSIS]]]☸
[[/span]]
[[span style="font-family: 'Nova Flat', cursive";]]"In place of a tongue, SCP-4161 has a USB 2.0 cable extruding from the lower larynx and protruding up through the esophagus, terminating in a male connector."[[/span]]
@@ @@
@@ @@
   [[/div]]

   [[div class="content-panel standalone series"]]
[[span style="font-family: 'Nova Flat', cursive; font-size: 150%";]]
**Chapter II**
@@ @@
//Three things cannot be long hidden: the sun, the moon, and the truth.//
[[/span]]
[[span style="font-family: 'Nova Flat', cursive; font-size: 120%";]]
☸[[[the-moons-stellar-companion|The Moon's Stellar Companion]]]☸
[[/span]]
[[span style="font-family: 'Nova Flat', cursive";]]"Gold columns rise above me endlessly, though I can see the very top as beings with hundreds of arms dance upon them to a silent rhythm."[[/span]]
[[span style="font-family: 'Nova Flat', cursive; font-size: 120%";]]
☸[[[SCP-4801|SCP-4801 - Ceto-vimutti:  Deliverance From Suffering]]]☸
[[/span]]
[[span style="font-family: 'Nova Flat', cursive";]]"Stripped bare, torn, sheared, and destroyed. And so now we can find a form far more refined. We have arrived."[[/span]]
@@ @@
@@ @@
